      <caption>
        <p>(a) Schematic diagram of the pipeline. (b) Volcano plot from using EPIC DNA methylation array. (c) Heatmap using top 100 CpGs normalized β values. (d) GO over-representation analysis result. (e) Pathway enrichment result using Reactome database and over representation analysis with BH-corrected <italic toggle="yes">P</italic>-value</p>
      </caption>
